snippet.title: Open Fortress: Deathmatch Gameplay, DM_Overkill and DM_Watchtower (June 2nd, 2019)
snippet.description:
Recorded by: Stachekip

"Video is at 720p 30fps because my CPU is from the stone age."

This sourcemod is pretty much in "open alpha" stages and things are very much subject to change as development progresses. One thing that will definitely stay constant however is the fast and fluid gameplay you see on display in Deathmatch mode.
